```

---

## 🔧 Core Capabilities

### 1. Network & Infrastructure Discovery
- **Subdomain enumeration** (passive & active techniques)
- **DNS intelligence** — Full record enumeration, historical analysis
- **TLS/SSL forensics** — Certificate transparency, JARM fingerprinting
- **IP reputation** — Multiple threat intelligence feeds
- **ASN & BGP mapping** — Infrastructure visualization

### 2. Web & Application Profiling
- **Technology stack detection** — Frameworks, libraries, CDN, email providers
- **Security posture audit** — Headers, cookies, exposed endpoints
- **Historical analysis** — Wayback Machine, cached pages
- **Source code search** — Public repositories, paste sites

### 3. Identity Intelligence
- **Username correlation** — 700+ platforms with false-positive filtering
- **Email verification** — 120+ platform registration checks
- **Social media analysis** — Content, connections, patterns
- **Professional footprint** — LinkedIn, GitHub, corporate domains
- **Breach data correlation** — Historical breach metadata

### 4. Relational Mapping
- **Cross-platform correlation** — Usernames, emails, avatars, bios
- **Recursive discovery** — Bio-extracted aliases (up to 4 hops)
- **Avatar perceptual hashing** — Visual identity matching
- **Temporal activity mapping** — Timezone inference from patterns
- **Interactive graph visualization** — D3.js relationship explorer

### 5. Dark Web Intelligence
- **Hidden service discovery** — Onion site enumeration
- **Marketplace & forum monitoring**
- **Threat actor tracking**

### 6. Threat Correlation
- **Malware & C2 detection** — IOC matching
- **Exploit & vulnerability correlation**
- **Ransomware group mapping**
- **Sanctions & compliance checks** — OFAC SDN integration

---

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

### Tools & Frameworks
| Category | Tools |
|----------|-------|
| **Domain Recon** | Subfinder, Amass, Assetfinder, Sublist3r |
| **DNS** | DNSRecon, Fierce, DNSDumpster |
| **Network** | Shodan, Censys, Nmap, Masscan |
| **Identity** | Sherlock, Maigret, Holehe, theHarvester |
| **Social** | Twint, Instaloader, Osintgram |
| **Graph** | Helix, Maltego, SpiderFoot |
| **OSINT Frameworks** | Recon-ng, OSINT Recon Suite |
| **AI Integration** | Claude, OpenRouter, NVIDIA NIM |

### Programming Languages & Libraries
```

Python 3.9+

· aiohttp, requests, dnspython
· cryptography, imagehash, Pillow
· NetworkX, D3.js (visualization)
· anthropic, openai (AI providers)

```

