⚖️ Legal & Ethical Framework

This framework is designed for authorized security assessments only.

Requirements before use:

· ✅ Written authorization from target organization/individual
· ✅ Compliance with all applicable laws and regulations
· ✅ Use of publicly accessible data only
· ❌ No active exploitation, injection, or brute-force
· ❌ No credential harvesting or social engineering
· ❌ No data storage without explicit consent

Ethical Guidelines:

· Respect privacy rights
· Protect findings appropriately
· Report vulnerabilities responsibly
· Do not use for harassment, stalking, or discrimination

Misuse of this framework is strictly prohibited. Aetherverse Intelligence Protocol assumes no liability for unauthorized use.

